content:
Tracks memory consumption during development activities and alerts when memory usage is high. Helps prevent out-of-memory issues and identify memory leaks.

```json
{
  "Notification": [
    {
      "hooks": [
        {
          "type": "command",
          "command": "MEM_USAGE=$(ps aux | grep -E 'node|python|java|ruby' | awk '{sum+=$4} END {print sum}' 2>/dev/null || echo '0'); if (( $(echo \"$MEM_USAGE > 50\" | bc -l 2>/dev/null || echo 0) )); then echo '⚠️ MEMORY: High memory usage detected ('$MEM_USAGE'%)'; fi; SWAP=$(free | grep Swap | awk '{print ($3/$2)*100}' 2>/dev/null || sysctl vm.swapusage 2>/dev/null | grep -oE '[0-9]+%' || echo '0'); if [[ \"${SWAP%\\%}\" -gt 50 ]]; then echo '⚠️ MEMORY: High swap usage ('$SWAP')'; fi"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```
